CABINET SECRETARIAT
(Department of Cabinet Affairs)
New Delhi, the 18th July 1964.
The undersigned is directed to state that, with effect from
today, July 18, 1964, Shri C. Subramaniam, Minister of Food &
Agriculture, will exercise overall supervision over the work of
the Ministry of Community Developm ent & Cooperation so as to
concentrate its activities on increased agricultural production.
( S.K. Mukherjee )
Joint Secretary to the Cabinet.
